* Tags and Categories

You can tagging packages freely.

** Tags

Tags indicates classifications of the package.
You can tag the package with a number of tags.

** Categories

Package administrator also able to add, remove package tags.
And set one tag as "Primary Tag".

Primary tag indicates the category of the package.

For example:
- Services_Foursquare :
-- Category : Services
-- Tags : API, Web Services, etc.
- HTML_CSS_Mobile:
-- Category : HTML
-- Tags : HTML, CSS, etc.

** Tag List

- [http://openpear.org/packages/tags]

